+<p><strong>Good Morning!</strong></p>
+<p>Today will be a hot, sunny day on the North Shore with highs in the 90s and expected to continue through tomorrow, Monday.&nbsp;</p>
+<p>It's a great day to take advantage of the surrounding lakes and rivers to cool off. Remember to stay hydrated and wear sun protection.</p>
+<p>If you're in the mood for a sweat treat, stop by the Warming Mug (just opened) inside the Registration Building to cool off with an ice cream cone or an iced espresso drink!</p>
+<p><strong>NOAA Weather Report:</strong> Sunny, with a high of 92. Calm wind.</p>
+<p><strong>Gondola Scenic Rides (10:00 AM- 5:00 PM)</strong>: Come experience the only Gondola in the Midwest! Enjoy breathtaking views of Lake Superior, then stop by the Summit Chalet for food, drinks, and some of the best overlooks on the North Shore.</p>
+<p><strong>Alpine Slide (11:00 AM-5:00 PM):</strong> The Alpine Slide is open today! Take a ride up the Bridge Lift and enjoy an exciting trip down the twists, turns, and dips of the track.&nbsp;</p>
+<p><strong>Summit Chalet: </strong>Bar 10:00 am - 4:30 pm &amp; Kitchen 11:00 am - 4:00 pm</p>
+<p><strong>Charlie's Alpine Bistro: </strong>Open Friday-Tuesday, 3:00 pm - 9:00 pm.</p>
+<p><strong>Pre-purchase Tickets</strong> <strong>Online (NEW Pick Up Boxes!):</strong> To make the most of your visit, we recommend purchasing your tickets online before you arrive. Once your purchase is complete, simply scan the barcode from your confirmation email at one of <strong>the automated pickup kiosks</strong> located to the right of the ticket windows or next to the Alpine Slide loading area. Your RFID cards will print instantly, so you can skip the ticket line and get straight to the fun.</p>
+<p><strong>Thank you for visiting Lutsen Mountains. We hope you have an amazing day on the mountain!</strong></p>
